title: Bodyguard
casts: Salman Khan, Kareena Kapoor, Raj Babbar, Asrani, Vidya Sinha, Hazel Keech, Chetan Hansraj, Salim Baig
description: Irked by her bodyguard, an heiress invents a secret admirer to throw him off his duties, but the plan may backfire when she falls for him.

title: Prem Ratan Dhan Payo
casts: Salman Khan, Sonam Kapoor, Anupam Kher, Neil Nitin Mukesh, Sanjay Mishra, Swara Bhaskar, Deepak Dobriyal, Arman Kohli, Manoj Joshi, Samaira Rao, Karuna Pandey, Sucheta Khanna
description: While recovering from an assassination attempt four days prior to his coronation, a stern prince is replaced by a joyful and generous doppelgänger.

title: Paharganj
casts: Lorena Franco, Bijesh Jayarajan, Neet Chowdhary, Rajeev Gaursingh, Karran Jeet, Rajesh Sharma, Gautam Kurup, Poonam Mathur, Salman Khan, Manish Devkush
description: In the underbelly of a Delhi neighborhood, a woman’s search for her missing lover collides with drugs, death and a coach grappling with his demons.

title: Mumbai Cha Raja
casts: Rahul Bairagi, Arbaaz Khan, Tejas Parvatkar, Dhanshree Jain, Salman Khan, Aftab Khan
description: This coming-of-age tale follows Rahul, a young boy growing up in a Mumbai slum whose alcoholic father abuses him and his mother.

title: Ready
casts: Salman Khan, Asin, Paresh Rawal, Mahesh Manjrekar, Anuradha Patel, Manoj Pahwa, Manoj Joshi, Puneet Issar, Sharat Saxena, Akhilendra Mishra, Zarine Khan, Arya Babbar
description: Bollywood superstar Salman Khan plays Prem, an heir to a perfume fortune who falls in love with the wrong woman in this romantic comedy.
